snippet.title: The Sims 3 Generations Expansion Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy a whole spectrum of rich life experiences with your Sims! With new celebrations, dramatic life events, and all-new ways for your Sims to express their creativity, The Sims 3 Generations is fun for all ages!

Pre-order your copy today and get ready to live every age to the fullest!

http://www.thesims3.com/games/ep4
